cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.ET, cs.SE 

The paper proposes a model predictive control based energy management system for interconnected microgrids, which involves optimization and distributed control. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the optimization problem is solved using a distributed augmented Lagrangian method. The paper also involves distributed computing, which could fall under cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The use of renewable energy sources and microgrids could also relate to cs.ET (Emerging Technologies) and cs.SE (Software Engineering).
